Here are things to consider before you begin:

1.	This application may take approximately 30 minutes to complete
2.	Please have digital copies of the following documents ready to upload:

Government issued photo identification (examples: State ID, Passport, Green Card, Military or Tribal Identification) for ALL Adult Household Members (18+ Years Old)

3.	Income documents  (examples: Benefit award letters, pay stubs, bank statements, etc.) from prior month for ALL Adult Household Members (18+ Years Old)
Are you the primary account holder completing this application for yourself and your household?
Please select one of the following:
